metadata.name: the dark ninja
metadata.description:
Only by standing at the top of the slum  can I see the miserable side of the city hidden in lights and wine.
Rises or falls of the city, the people get the worst of it. 
"Action Engage."
————————————————
只有在此处，我才能看到隐藏在灯红酒绿中的悲惨一面。
无论城市兴衰，人们总在受苦。
“开始行动”
